{"tid":55980,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚喺廟街有隻老雞來搭我搏頭","createTime":"2016-12-26T20:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T16:15:46.000Z","uid":18605,"like":512,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e06ad958c676616046760b1d3788b239fd458177","tid":55980,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:50:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟尋晚行過廟街，有隻老雞過來搵生意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :老雞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :靚仔，聖誕過後乜咁寂寞呀，唔係要扑性day架咩？定還是想要搵人曳曳呀。<br />\n<br />\n我上下打量隻老雞，見到臉上嘅濃妝早已因為老化鬆弛嘅肌膚而起哂粒粒，望落一啲見到一條明顯係谷出來嘅事業線，腳就著左薄到接近透明嘅肉絲，身穿露肩聖誕紅衣嘅佢，身上散發住陣陣驅風油嘅氣味，令人精神為之一振。<br />\n<br />\n佢迷離嘅雙眼貶一眨眼，仿佛就喺度講緊，我空虛，我寂寞，我凍。眼捷毛嘅抖動仿佛喺度訴說心靈嘅空洞，求我快啲來填滿佢。<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻，我同老雞嘅距離，只有10厘米，我知道，係佢啦。如果呢刻我出手，可能有無限嘅未來，但係，我選擇離開，因為我想將呢一刻嘅風景，永存於心裡。愛因斯坦話過，我只求永存嘅回憶，而非剎那嘅存在。<br />\n<br />\n於是我回答<br />\n「要翻工，不了。」<br />\n<br />\n佢聽到呢句之後，對波震左一震，仿佛估唔到會得到咁嘅回覆。雙目原有嘅色彩變得暗淡無光，就連驅風油嘅味道，都好似淡左。<br />\n<br />\n正當我想拂袖而去嘅時候，手臂傳來一陣冰涼嘅感覺，我一轉過頭，見到佢眼泛淚光，用楚楚可憐嘅眼神望住我，講：「三十蚊，1Q。」<br />\n<br />\n30蚊......1Q？<br />\n<br />\n呢句說話好似一鎚鍾左落我心口度咁。<br />\n<br />\n咩話......30蚊......1Q？<br />\n<br />\n回望過去，做左28年處男，身邊個個朋友都攬緊女，我仲係一個處男......之前果10年聖誕節落老蘭收到果啲免費condom 我一個都未用過！！！！望住派condom過幾個𡃁模，笑住咁同我講：今晚玩得開心啲呀。我對得住佢地咩！！！嗯，無錯啦，今晚我就要用行動來回應佢地，今晚過後我唔再係處男！！！<br />\n<br />\n我用堅定嘅意志同佢講：「我要10Q。」<br />\n<br />\n佢聽到都呆一呆，但好快又回復笑容：「10Q?你得唔得呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「試下咪知囉。」我用自信嘅態度來回應佢<br />\n<br />\n「好哇，咁請客人跟我過來。」<br />\n<br />\n我跟住佢行，穿過大街小巷，街上嘅人都向我投上奇特嘅目光，佢嘅短裙，隨住冬日嘅微風擺動，若隱若現嘅肉色包屎忽底褲令我更加興奮，佢走過嘅每一寸道路，都殘留住驅風油嘅味道。<br />\n<br />\n「上樓啦。」我望一望目的地，一個大大嘅粉紅色光管正掛喺頭頂，我知道，今晚......將會係翻雲覆雨嘅一夜。<br />\n<br />\n我跟住佢上樓，行左兩層，由下而上咁望到佢著嘅底褲，裙下風光一覽無違，加上驅風油嘅氣球，將眼前光景再一步昇華。<br />\n<br />\n「到啦。」我地企喺黑色鐵門前面，佢伸手將鐵門慢慢推開，我吞一吞口水，準備迎接人生新嘅一頁，道門完全打開哂，眼前嘅風景，完全令我震撼到一個極點，我只可以以o嘴來形容當時場景。<br />\n<br />\n佢竟然......佢竟然......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">帶左我去打桌球呀！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"71c51f9848044c2ec2cc24df82ed67e0ae459ce8","tid":55980,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯有用condom 笠住Q棍開心打洞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n好文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e041866b73bc4a6a7f6349edf63fa13fdb269ab","tid":55980,"uid":28190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:57:53.000Z","msg":"有是咁的，80分"},{"pid":"3cbc4074b9ea23400ac136ad0744d2665db76327","tid":55980,"uid":9098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:59:18.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪有開台果位？過埋嚟連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f29c58999848c1cfdb9497a72b775246dae47a0","tid":55980,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:59:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"e108690c4dced93758bc46af6f2d5101decbe072","tid":55980,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯有用condom 笠住Q棍開心打洞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n好文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係即興寫嘅文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寫完原來已經就5點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞓先"},{"pid":"20b65eec79198c7bce4ec464e46021b863f54d53","tid":55980,"uid":5272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:00:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a965c65ab359625b4a66c085336b381ee29cb4","tid":55980,"uid":35393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高質"},{"pid":"b052e9fc3602cb5f1b4998f685a429444c113db9","tid":55980,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打係咪有開台果位？過埋嚟連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果位係沙填入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (唔諗打)門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我認個名嘅由來係因為佢</span></span>"},{"pid":"f6161d6c1087940c74ea8d99cd018a23ad7f4737","tid":55980,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打係咪有開台果位？過埋嚟連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果位係沙填入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (唔識打)門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我認個名嘅由來係因為佢</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"71c7ce08bb33843e8f22066176a1950c07630b7d","tid":55980,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝你睇完我篇垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf107ee917b0fb0ea57263db01cd71060f086683","tid":55980,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca60cb0820693d7a6b026e91c9abf9d6fecc51f5","tid":55980,"uid":18449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高汁"},{"pid":"6c31b0c620c57e484e73af033018609af7ab7fee","tid":55980,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2164bc0726bcc60bea2eb0b1d9069d23fee076a1","tid":55980,"uid":7004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:20:21.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8663598ec4da1d5ca7bda61e1d0d8deaf7f439","tid":55980,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:20:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88466e9e251e9b0b4514d08e1596faea15dc1f68","tid":55980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:54:17.000Z","msg":"連登第一篇潮文"},{"pid":"63b67d2c8244f10a4a3e60cabcdf642c17356cdf","tid":55980,"uid":32932,"like":